title: Midnight Oil
lyrics:
I got pretty colors for your actions
I will lay them down before you
I will send them to you when I can
Oh, up, love, save,
Wait for me, desperate loyal

Open up your mind to me

Don't burn the midnight oil



I got foreign letters for your passions

I will lay them down before you

I got better notions for the next one



Oh, up, love, save,

Wait for me, desperate loyal

Open up your mind to me

Don't burn the midnight oil
